original: Larsson, Anders Fredrik, tf. fängelsedirektör, Norrköping, f. 4/10/96 i Karlskrona av flaggunderoff. Anton L. o. Augusta Månsson. G. 27 m. farm. kand. Alvida Johanna Sörensen. Barn: Börje f. 31. — Stud:ex. i Karlskrona 16. Assist, v. fångv:anst. i Karlskrona, Falun, Härianda, Malmö, Härnösand, Upps. m. fl. 18-30, förste assist, v. Långholmen 31, tf. dir. v. cen-tralfäng. i Norrköp. fr. 37.
translated: Larsson, Anders Fredrik, acting prison director, Norrköping, born on October 4th, 1896 in Karlskrona to ensign Anton L. and Augusta Månsson. Married on the 27th with Alvida Johanna Sörensen, who holds a degree in agriculture. Children: Börje, born in 1931. Completed high school in Karlskrona in 1916. Worked as an assistant at prisons in Karlskrona, Falun, Härianda, Malmö, Härnösand, Uppsala, and other locations from 1918 to 1930. Became head assistant at Långholmen in 1931, and acting director at the central prison in Norrköping from 1937 onwards.
